Steps for the Creation Git ID and Working with the Git Hub

Step -1 
Create Email  ID > 
Step -2 
Enter the credentials in the Git hub login page >
Step -3
For the verification purpose Git Will send us the Email in having Verificatiom Code
Step -4 
On the top side of the github page we will find the pop up button named as Create Repository
Step -5
Click on the Button to create the repo.
Step -6
As we create the reposotiory, we will find the option
Step -7
We will get a option of create new file
Step -8
Add the appropriate data in the file
